  "body": "<p>One of our creative partners, <a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/HelloAm\">Hello Am</a> shared some of their digital goodies with us. I love the <a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/162352153/inspirational-quote-inspirational-poster?ref=shop_home_active\">Let's Have Adventures Under the Stars print</a> and requested it in black for Jack's room. Since I don't like to waste paper, here is how I laid it out to print. I plan on using the others in Project Life.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/c21cd4e2fd8600af.png?v=1782532988\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Then I trimmed it and placed it right into the Ikea frame.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/45ee3dc356581517.jpg?v=1782532991\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Once we get a chance, we will add it to the wall next to the <a href=\"http://mayahayuk.com/\">Maya Hayuk</a> piece that is already hanging.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/47a060144932309b.jpg?v=1782532993\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>And here is a message from <a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/HelloAm\">HelloAm</a>: <strong>For craft enthusiasts who love our paper designs, we have a Xmas special you'll love: </strong><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/168482885/sale-buy-3-get-2-free-digital-paper?ref=listing-shop-header-0\">Buy 3, get 2 FREE!</a> <a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/168469910/sale-buy-2-get-1-free-digital-paper?ref=listing-shop-header-1\">Buy 2, get 1 FREE!</a> This is a Xmas special promotion by HelloAm and it ONLY applies to the DIGITAL SCRAPBOOKING section in HelloAm. See my entire digital paper range <a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/HelloAm?section_id=13922990\">here</a>. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . <strong>Come 2014, I promise it will be beautiful</strong> We have designed a calendar full of love quotes! This calendar features 12 all time favorite love quotes from the month of January to December. This product is a physical product which will be mailed to you upon purchase. See it <a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/168355846/2014-wall-calendar-love-quote-wall-art?ref=shop_home_feat\">here</a>. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .<strong> </strong><strong>Subscribe to HelloAm</strong><strong>, </strong>and all subscribers will get a set of free digital paper.</p><p>In the column \"how did you get to know about HelloAM\", simply fill in \"Amy\"</p><p><strong>HelloAm is now blogging and sharing our inspiration</strong> <a href=\"http://helloamdesign.blogspot.sg/\">here</a>. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . <strong>HelloAm would love to engage you on our Facebook.</strong> Get to know about our current promotions, freebies and latest updates. Like us <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HelloAmDesign\">here</a>. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p><p>THANK YOU HELLO AM! Interested in sponsoring a spot for December or January? Email us: hello(at)amytangerine(dot)com</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
